CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 12, 1956, pg. A25, reads: "New Links - A trio of charming Pittsburghers was initiated into the Links, Inc., at the home of Lillian W. Brown in pretty ceremonies. Left to right: Mrs. Robert Bolden, Mrs. Earl Childs and Mrs. W. Augustus Cyrus who will add their talents to the popular group. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. Robert Bolden, Mrs. Earl Childs, and Mrs. W. Augustus Cyrus posed in home of Lillian W. Brown with brick fireplace
